      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 987.1 Cayman S featuring the 3.4L M97 flat-six powerplant. This mid-engine masterpiece delivers 295 hp through a short-throw 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by the factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), providing exceptional lateral stability and precise turn-in. Maintenance is up to date, including a preventative IMS bearing retrofit and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. The hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback modern EPS systems lack. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent bore-scoping and oil analysis\u2014confirm a healthy, high-revving engine ready for the canyons.",
